title: Where Does Brooklyn Go From Here?
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring David Jacoby and Izzy Gutierrez! On today's show: Where do the Nets, Kevin Durant, and Kyrie Irving stand after replacing Steve Nash with Ime Udoka? Should the Clippers and Warriors panic about their cold starts? Plus, what's the ceiling for the Cavs, Pelicans, and Blazers?
